{
  "info": {
    "name": "AgroBridge API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for AgroBridge agricultural traceability platform.\n\n## Features\n- Authentication with JWT\n- Batch traceability management\n- Producer management\n- Event tracking\n- Reports generation\n- Notifications\n\n## Getting Started\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Import the environment file\n3. Run the 'Login' request to get access token\n4. Start exploring the API!",
